title: Manoosh Pizzeria
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Mediterranean, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Lebanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A Lebanese style pizzeria that also serves wraps, breads, and hot desserts. Offers a number of vegan choices that are marked with an SV, including a pizza topped with faux bacon and Daiya cheese. Vegan possibilities also in wraps, dips, sides, salads. Staff understands veganism and will adjust a menu item for you - ask. Also another restaurant at 1/465 Illawarra Rd, Marrickville 2204.
